{
  "title": "Spicy Light Mediterranean Tuna Salad",
  "description": "A refreshing and spicy tuna salad with Mediterranean flavors, featuring bay leaves and a crunchy tadka. Perfect for a light lunch or snack.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
